## SS 3c. Extract Post Content (after navigating to post page)

Returns the post author and text. Run this BEFORE commenting on any post you navigated to. Use the returned `author` and `text` to inform your comment — your comment MUST directly address this specific post's topic.

```javascript
browser.act({
  kind: "evaluate",
  fn: `async () => {
    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000));
    var authorEl = document.querySelector('.update-components-actor__title span span');
